    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>
                    <sic>sunday</sic>
                </date>
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Decr 18<hi rend="underline">th</hi> 1835</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I should have <sic>aswered</sic> yours had I anything<lb/> of
                importance to write but as I wish you should hear from me<lb/> now and then, I must
                say we are all well <sic>accept</sic>
                <persName>Mrs Depass</persName><lb/> has her old complains again last
                        <date><sic>sunday</sic></date>
                <persName>Mr Tylor</persName> of <placeName>Richmond</placeName><lb/> my old
                    <sic>neghbour</sic> paid us a visit he was on his way to
                        <sic><placeName>philadelphia</placeName></sic><lb/> but the river being
                frozen, he <sic>stopt</sic> here and returned to <placeName>Rich</placeName><lb/> on
                        <date><sic>thursday</sic></date> he particularly inquired about you and
                desired to<lb/> be remembered to you, he also related the fight of
                    <persName>Myer</persName> &amp; <persName>Cohen</persName><lb/> that
                    <persName>Mrs Cohen</persName> was the cause of it, she is on
                    <persName>Myer</persName> side, <persName>Tylor</persName><lb/> also said that
                he believes it is owing on acct of <persName>Mrs Cohen</persName> to be<lb/>
                inclined to the christian church and <persName>Mr Cohen</persName> against it<lb/>
                well that is no doubt with me, because when she was<lb/> here last year <add>?</add>
                she went <add>Hebrew</add> night to the church, and as<lb/> for the <add>?</add> he
                is no better, pray let me know how are all<lb/> my friends the
                    <persName>Peixottos</persName>
                <sic>familia</sic> and how do you feel this cold<lb/> winter, I would advise you to
                have a pair of woolen <sic>sogs</sic>, put<lb/> over your shoes when you write to
                your Brother &amp; sister give my<lb/> love to them, how is <persName>Mrs
                    Hart</persName>, do you go to <persName>Mr L Philips</persName> if so<lb/>
                remember me to him &amp; her. I am getting <sic>Quite</sic> a prudent man<lb/> last
                night, I was at <persName>Ben Cohen</persName> and did not stay later than one a
                clock<lb/> if I could think of any thing to add I would do so as I cannot<lb/> I
                remain your friend &amp; &amp; <persName role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName></p>
            <p>your Aunt <persName>Mr Depass</persName>
                <persName>Abby David</persName> send <sic>there</sic> love to you remember me<lb/>
                kindly to <persName>Mr &amp; Mrs Peixotto</persName>
                <persName>Simah</persName>
                <persName>Rachel</persName>
                <persName>Betty</persName> and the young gentlemen<lb/> and all my friends</p>
            <p><persName>Mrs Etting</persName> has been very unwell, but is <sic>Quite</sic> better
                they send <sic>there</sic><lb/> respects to you, <persName>Mr E Cohen</persName> is
                gone to <placeName>Charlestown</placeName> and will not be back<lb/> till the
                    <sic>midle</sic> of <date>January</date>
                <persName>Mrs Cohen</persName>
                <sic>Desires</sic> to be remembered to you<lb/> if you see <persName>Miss Frances
                    Chamberlain</persName> give our respects to her<lb/> we heard that <persName>Mrs
                    Zeporo Seixas</persName> was <sic>wery</sic> sick, have you heard<lb/>
                <add>?</add> if so let us know <add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="The page seems to have a portion cut off at the bottom."/>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>to the Care of <persName>A. C Peixotto Esqr</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>single</p>
        </body>
